## Patterns

### Feature Structure
```
src/features/<feature-name>/
├── components/       # UI components
├── hooks/           # Business logic hooks
├── api/             # API calls
├── types.ts         # Shared types
├── index.ts         # Public exports
└── README.md        # Feature documentation
```

### Business Logic
- Pure functions for calculations
- Side effects in hooks/actions
- Domain events for cross-feature communication
- Feature flags for gradual rollouts

### Data Flow
- Server → API → Hook → Component
- Optimistic updates where appropriate
- Cache invalidation strategy per feature

## Constraints

### DO NOT
- Share internal state between features directly
- Put feature logic in shared components
- Bypass API layer for data access
- Couple features tightly

## Watch

### Auto-alerts
- New feature without README → suggest
- Circular dependency between features → block
- Feature >50 files → suggest splitting
- Untested business logic → warn

